      <h2 class="subtitle">CIVILIAN DEPARTMENT</h2>
      <div class="section">
        <div class="section-img">
          <img style="display: none;" id="civLogo" class="circle" src="/images/civ-logo.jpg" alt="Civ Logo">
          <img id="civLogoGif" class="circle" src="/images/civ-logo-gif.gif" alt="Civ Logo Gif">
        </div>
        <div class="section-text left">
          <p>Civilian Department (Civs), is where you can work jobs, get arrested, commit crimes...Everyday! This
